data.description: Price Improved! Bring your checkbook! Spacious Kitchen with Large Pantry and Laundry Room for extra storage.  Breakfast Bar is perfect to entertain family and friends. Sliding Glass Doors in the Kitchen lead to the Screened Lanai with all-day Lake Views and Evening Sunsets. Screened Lanai Door offers easy access to any owner's Pet-Friendly community. The Den offers an area for an open office, hobby room or another tv sitting area.  The Master Suite combines a Spacious Bedroom with a Walk-in Closet, and a Master Bathroom with Two Sinks for Busy Mornings, and an Easy to Clean Shower with Corner Seating.  Slider Glass Doors in master open to the screened lanai.  This split floor plan allows privacy for the 2nd Bedroom and 2nd Bathroom with tub and shower combo. Nearby Carport No. 103.  Bermuda Palms is a solidly built, concrete block, condo building built in 2004, has tile roofs and remains a Low Fee community. This location is home to the best schools. Enjoy the community pool, spa and picnic areas of Bermuda Palms all year long. Call for your appointment today.
